    # Settings Page Implementation Review

    ## 1. Mockup Fidelity
    - ✅ Screenshots generated and compared against mockups.
    - ✅ Layout structure, spacing, colors, and tab order match the mockups.
    - ✅ Component styles, typography, border radius, and padding align with
